Name: Play Top Frag
About the game: Play Top Frag is a training tool designed to measure, train and improve your skills on first-person shooter games. It measures qualities and player skills that are required in a first-person shooter, for example hand-eye coordination, reaction time, memory, hearing, color sight and other things. The tests are performed in a FPS-styled setting. Play Top Frag measures and logs all the individual training sessions, so users can monitor their progress over time.
